{"id": 3056, "genre": 1001, "title": "对你来说，啥样的生活算是有「自己的空间」？", "description": "你都是通过哪些日常细节，帮自己划出一块小小的「自我区域」的？（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 1682, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201911112240180nyZEojhfXTQNwpK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-11T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 349441, "content": "早起半小时，就多了半小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671066}, {"id": 349446, "content": "吃饭的时候可以安心看着综艺或视频；\n睡觉前有着两小时可以戴着耳机进行阅读没人打扰；\n周末可以睡个大早上，不用着急翻看手机消息；\n懒懒散散躺在床上，天气好就拿着相机出去拍照、录视频。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515489}, {"id": 349449, "content": "有独处的时间\n不被外界摆布", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665042}, {"id": 349451, "content": "做自己喜欢的事，不被别人左右", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559528}, {"id": 349453, "content": "经济自由 有个特别爱自己的老婆 去世界看看 身上有钱 身边有人 去最美的地方看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671166}, {"id": 349456, "content": "有一个自己不用顾虑的场合", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434374}, {"id": 350763, "content": "可以安静的窝在飘窗上看2小时书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588249}, {"id": 349500, "content": "休息天不被工作群以及领导骚扰的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671231}, {"id": 349501, "content": "躺在沙发上歪成各种形状看剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661643}, {"id": 349509, "content": "就算有室友也不会干涉自己的作息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 349515, "content": "有那么一刻，是什么都不用想的。或者是走在路上，或者是躺在床上，可以闭上眼睛，或盯着某一个地方。什么都不做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671320}, {"id": 349275, "content": "除了睡觉，每天能有一段时间不需要回复手机消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349276, "content": "吃饭的时候能找到一张单人座，不用拼桌那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349534, "content": "完全封闭安静的房间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671470}, {"id": 349279, "content": "就算不是一个人住，也至少得有一个单独的房间", "image": null, "praise_count": 326, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 349280, "content": "一个人住，跟爸妈/对象/室友一起不算", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351328, "content": "没有人来打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560500}, {"id": 349282, "content": "即使手机没电了，也不急去充电。", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655378}, {"id": 349284, "content": "经济自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 237, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618604}, {"id": 349285, "content": "放自己的音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484079}, {"id": 349286, "content": "想安静放空一会的时候，有自己的小角落", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334072}, {"id": 349287, "content": "降噪耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525473}, {"id": 349288, "content": "厕所隔间", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335668}, {"id": 349289, "content": "当心里不舒服时可以发泄", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596623}, {"id": 349292, "content": "能按自己的想法做自己想做的事情而不用操心打扰别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 556191}, {"id": 349293, "content": "戴着耳机一个人走在大街上，走走停停……", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670712}, {"id": 349294, "content": "想要安静独处的时候，没有外界打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630427}, {"id": 349806, "content": "有一个自己的小空间，烦躁的时候，没有打扰的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672494}, {"id": 349295, "content": "一山，一人，一狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132890}, {"id": 349296, "content": "老婆聚餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774444}, {"id": 349297, "content": "老婆入睡后...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774444}, {"id": 349553, "content": "有自己独立的空间 有很大的地板可以滚来滚去 有地毯可以舒服的躺在上面 有落地灯可以让我在地毯上安静的看书 一整面墙书架  散落一地的书  静静地入眠", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664151}, {"id": 349298, "content": "准时下班", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573736}, {"id": 349299, "content": "可以穿睡衣不穿bra的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670066}, {"id": 349555, "content": "做自己偏爱的事，没有时间的焦虑，没有收入的焦虑，不在乎成败，不需要对任何人负责，不需要向任何人解释原因。\r\nJust do it , because I like it！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671578}, {"id": 349302, "content": "每天都能有一些独处的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670733}, {"id": 349303, "content": "每天有时间做自己喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434675}, {"id": 349304, "content": "公司有小会议室可以摸会鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580075}, {"id": 349306, "content": "在床上发呆的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460417}, {"id": 349307, "content": "可以无干扰看自己喜欢的书", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657468}, {"id": 349308, "content": "可能就现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458149}, {"id": 349309, "content": "不盖楼不砍一刀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353555}, {"id": 349311, "content": "当然是财务自由，可惜我没有 o(╥﹏╥)o ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604076}, {"id": 349312, "content": "自由时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670311}, {"id": 349313, "content": "大学宿舍里拉上床帘的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056087}, {"id": 349315, "content": "安安静静不被打扰的睡眠", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460689}, {"id": 349316, "content": "安静无人的空间和自由支配的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662600}, {"id": 349317, "content": "不用上班的时候，一个人在家躺尸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 349318, "content": "泡在图书馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 349575, "content": "有自己的房间，不管租还是买，可以有决定权，随意安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671748}]}